data.description: Situated on a shy third of an acre, this property offers a level & usable space. Pergo hardwood floors. The kitchen & bathroom features slab granite counters & custom cabinets. Custom built-in bedroom dresser. Upstairs, 2 spacious beds await, along with a full bath, providing privacy & comfort for guests. Downstairs, a half bath & laundry room add convenience to your daily routine. The open kitchen seamlessly flows into the family room, creating a perfect space for gatherings & entertaining. The expansive & level yard beckons for outdoor gatherings & recreational activities. The attached garage on the main level not only provides convenient parking but also boasts a bonus room for your creative endeavors. A must see!
